FBIS4-41194 "drsov121_d_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Situation Stabilizing in Ingushetia-Ossetia Situation Stabilizing in Ingushetia-Ossetia LD2206141894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206141894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Reports from the zone of the Ossetian-Ingush conflict, where the state of emergency was extended until 30 June by the Russian president's edict, say the situation there is stabilizing. This has also been confirmed by military sources. No interethnic conflicts have been registered there in the past day. The Russian peacekeeping forces, jointly with the local law enforcement bodies, continue to ensure that the state of emergency is being observed.
